<sup>(34-35)</sup> Nunalget, mangteghalget akikneghmegteki nunatengllu mangteghatengllu, allgeghtateng manit apostle‑enun tuunaqegkangit. Enkaam ugpeqat sameng aklunghata manilitaqegkangit, tawaten kina alngunak aklumangilnguq.
(-)
<sup>(36-37)</sup> Joseph tawanlenguq, Cyprus‑eghmii, Levi‑em kingungha, ellnganllu akikluku nunani tuunegkaa allgeghtani apostle‑enun. Apostle‑et atiqaat Barnabas‑meng whaten pisimeng, “Kayemesta.”
