Zebulun‑em ramkenganeng, 12,000‑nguftut,Joseph‑em ramkenganeng, 12,000‑nguftut,Benjamin‑em ramkenganeng, 12,000‑nguftut.
Yulgughuteghllaget Maniguqangat KiyaghneqTaam kingunganeng esghaghanka uglapestaaghllaget yulghuteghllaget kitum alngunak kestepagningilkangi! Tamaghhiitneng pinguftut nunataaneng, ramkeneng, yugneng, ulunengllu. Nekevghatnguftut umiilgusim aqumutam, Penniighaghaamllu sivugkenkun. Qiipaghaalluteng qatelghiineng, tugumiighlutengllu palm‑em uqfigan avayiitneng.
Akilghuuteghllagtut,“Yugulilleq Kiyaghnemta pikaa umiilgusigni aqumutagni aqumgalghii, Penniighaghaamllu!”
Qamaglluteng yaqulget nekevuutut uvitangitni umiilgusim aqumutam, elder‑etlu, estamatlu unguvalghiit. Taagken sekequutut nunamun sivungakun umiilgusim aqumutam, manigughaat Kiyaghneq.
Piit,“Amen! Kiyaghneghput tamaghhaghmi usuqligu,nighughqelligu, iyamsiqayugvikligu,quulvaghligu qayughllak ellnganguuq peghqinellelek,aghtughyaghqaanghillelek, iknaqelleleklu.Ellnga tawatetuq quunperugllak kenlengunaan!Amen!”
Taagken ataasim elder‑eneng aaptaanga, “Kinkungaawat qatelghiimeng qiipaghaghngalghiit, nakenllu pingwaat?”
Kiimsighaqa, “Yuguniiq, elpek liisimakaten.” Elder‑em piinga, “Taakunguut suflughutkat seghleliighrukutaaghllagmeng. Penniighaghaam aawakun aghvigluki qiipaghateng, qateghtestekaqiit.
Iyatiqnanighllequt,nalighmeng meqsugyugnanighllequt.Siqinghem nalighmeng alngunak uguqnaghllalghiim ugunnaanghitii.
Penniighaghaq umiilgusim aqumutam saaghwanilnguq penniighniightekelleqaat.Maghyaghqughlleqii sengngulghiinun meghnun unguvallelitikayugnun, Kiyaghneghemllu quningightughlleqii.”
Maaghraghvinliitangi Seal‑ellghemPenniighaghaam qelpeghtaqngamigu maaghraghvinliitanga seal‑ellghem, qilagmi qallegnanighwaaghutut entaqun aflum avellghatun tagkaan.
Taagken esghaghanka taakut maaghraghvinlek yaqulget nekevghalghiit Kiyaghneghem sivungakun. Tamaghhaghmeng qalghightaatenguutut.
Taagken ilanga yaqulek, tugumiilek gold‑meng sagneghmeng, tagiluni nekevuq aghqefigegni. Tuunegkaat incense‑elghutmeng ilatesqelluki qamaglluki yughiitnun Kiyaghneghem yugan. Yaqulgem llii gold‑egnun aghqefigegnun sivunganilnguuk umiilgusim aqumutam.
Incense‑em agepsaa mayughtuq maligulluni yughallghitgun Kiyaghneghem yugita. Mayughtut Kiyaghneghmun sagneghmeng yaqulgem tugumiighaneng.
Taagken yaqulgem, tuguluku sagneq, imighaa kenghaneng aghqefigem. Sagneghem imii miluutii nunamun. Enkaam kallugughteghllagtuq, kavlegtaghllagtuq, nighwaaghpagtaghllagtuq, nunallu ufsuguteghllagtuq.
QalghightaatetTaagken maaghraghvinlek yaqulget, qalghightaatelget yataaghqut qalghightinaluteng.
Sivuliim yaqulgem qalghightaatni qalghightaa. Taagken kaftekragenkuk, kenghenkuk akumlutek aawmeng nunamun miluutagket. Enkaam pingayughqellgha nunam paneghtuq, pingayughqellghitlu uqfiget paneghtut, qamagllutengllu sungaghyulghiit vegaaghet paneghtut.
Tuunglighhaan yaqulgem qalghightaatni qalghightaa. Taagken sangwaa naayghaghllagsugnilnguq kumaghugngalghii, miluutaat kelliinun. Enkaam pingayughqellgha kelliim aawgughtuq.
Pingayughqellghit kelliinilnguut unguvalghiit tuquut, pingayughqellghitlu angyaghpaget naafqengngwaaghii.
Pingayiitangita yaqulgem qalghightaatni qalghightaa. Taagken ighaleqetaaghllak, kumaghughngalghii torch‑etun, qilagameng ifkaghtuq pingayughqellghitgun kiiwetlu sengngulghiitlu meghet.
Aatgha ighaleqetaaghem “Sungaghni”. Pingayughqellgha meghem sungaghnightekaq enkaam yulghuteghllaget meghluteng tuqukat qayughllak meq sungaghnightekaalghii.
Estamiitangita yaqulgem qalghightaatni qalghightaa. Taagken saam tenpii siqineq, tanqiq, ighaleqataaghetlu, enkaam pingayughqellghi mamlegtii. Pingayughqellgha aghneghem mamlegtaa, pingayughqellghallu unugem.
Esghaghaqallu nagaqughaqallu qawaagpak tengaalghii quulvani, iglagtuluni pilghii, “Seghleghwaaghunaqnguuq! Seghleghwaaghunaqnguuq! Seghleghwaaghunaqnguuq! Kinguliit pingayut yaqulget qalghighhnaqegkumegteki qalghightaateteng, taagken elngaatall seghlepestaaghunaqnguuq yugnun nunami kiyaghlleghhiit tamaani pilleghni!”
Taagken tallimiitangita yaqulgem qalghightaatni qalghightaa. Esghaghaqa ighaleqetaaq ifkaqaq qilagameng nunamun, key‑litkaaftuqlu qelpeghtesqelluku asilighneghilnguq laawaaq.
Ighaleqetaaghem qelpeghtaa asilighneghilnguq laawaaq. Tesamaken agepsuq aanuq katam agepsaatun egllughllagem repall siqineqlu qilagallu mamlegtaa agepsum.
Taagken agepsumeng aanleghaatut locust‑elghutet, nunamunllu ukigtuutut. Kaapigaqleghutekat yugneng, katam scorpion‑et kaapiiqellghistun.
Ungipaatkaalghiit locust‑et naafqefqiita vegaaghet pisqelluki nalighmeng sungaghyuget nunivagseghat nalighmeng alngunak uqfiget. Aqnightesqegkiillu tamaakunginaat yuget Kiyaghneghem nalluniillghilkangi qawiitgun.
Locust‑enun tuququghtesnaniqii tamaakut yuget, taawanginaq ikfiqesteghllagestesqegkii tallimanun tanqinun. Scorpion‑et kaapellghistun yuget ikfiqeghllakat.
Taakuni tallimani tanqini tamaakut yuget tuquyupigllequt, iwernga tuqupagningillequt. Yuget tuqunaqeghllagllequt, iwernga tuqunaanghitut.
Locust‑et esghaqaaluteng kuunistun ayuqut pilluwamun yataaghqegkat. Naasqwitniteftut llangaqa gold‑et qaghpat, gginiitlu yuget gginiistun ayuqluteng.
Nuyiit aghnat nuyiistun ayuqluteng, gguutngitlu lion‑et gguutngistun ayuqluteng.
Yugusimegteggun qaltelguftut esghaqaaluteng savikenghaaghet sakimagiitat. Yaqwghitallu sulugtallghit llangaqa chariot‑et kuunituqat sukeralghiit pilluwamun.
Papelguftut scorpion‑estun kaapikayugmeng. Enkaam tallimanun tanqinun yuget ikfiqesteghllagiit papegmeggneng kapughluki.
Umiilelguftut igleghutilghii ellngitneng, yaqulguftuq esghaamakistenga asilighneghilnguum laawaaghem. Hebrew‑stun aatgha Abaddon, Greek‑estun Apollyon, (whaten pisiq, “Naafqiista”).
Sivuliq seghlepestaaghllak alpagtuq, taam kingunganeng paninang maalghuk seghlepestaaghllagek piyaghqaaguk.
Aghvinliitanga QalghightallghemTaagken aghvinliitangita yaqulgem qalghightaatni qalghightaa. Nagaqughaqa ma gold‑egneng aghqefigegneng estamaneng sighunelgegneng tekerqamegnekun Kiyaghneghem sivunganilnguuk.
Taam mem aleghqughaa aghvinliitangat yaqulget qalghightaatelek. Pikaa, “Itemutiki estamat yaqulget asighqengngalghiit kiigwllagegni Euphrates‑egni!”
Ungipaataanga uglaghtalangitneng kuunitgun igleghlleghhiit pilluwaghtet, 200 million‑nguftut.
Esghaghwaallemkun esghaghanka kuunit, igleghutistengitlu. Sakimagiitiit kenghestun kaviteftut, sapphire‑estun sungaghyukegteftut, sulphur‑estun, yellow‑nguftut. Kuunit naasqwit lion‑et naasqwistun ayuqeftut, qaanghitneng aanut keneq, agepsuq, sulphur‑a.
Taakutgun pingayutgun naafqiilleghllagteggun tuququghiit pingayughqellghi yuget. Kuunit qaanghitneng aanleghaatut keneq, agepesuq, sulphur‑a.
Kuunit aghtughyaghqaanghillelguut qaanghitnillu paapgitnillu. Paapgit nemeghyastun ayuqelghiit naasqulget kiitiqusiit yugnun.
Ilangi tamaakut yuget tuqutellghilkangit tamaakut naafqiilleghllaget, avuteghqumangilnguut pegsugumangilkangit kiyaghnengllaqateng. Manigughnaniimangitiit tughneghaat, kiyaghnengllaqatlu ulimaaghet gold‑meng, silver‑meng, siilumeng, uyghagmeng, unaghsimengllu. Tamaakut esghaasaghqaanghilnguut, nagaquusaghqaanghilnguut, nalighmeng piyugyaghqaanghilnguut.
Talwa avuteghqutkumangilkangit yugtalleteng, alignaghtaalleteng, nengughtegpenateng atuqutelleghteng, nalighmeng teglegniilleteng.
Yaquleklu Iimgatlu IgaghhaatTaagken esghaghaqa ilanga aghtiigateghllak yaqulek ukilghii qilagmeng. Pilugugngaftuq qilagwaaghmeng, naasqwan qulangani agluk, gginaa siqineghtun kuukgulluni, ighukeklu kumaghulghiistun pillar‑estun ayuqlutek.
Tugumiiqeftii iimgat igaghhaat qelpalnguut. Aghenqigneghet itegani tuutestii kelliim meghan qaayngakun, saghumigneghetlu itegani tuutestii quutkun.
Iglagtupiglluni akilghuuguq lion‑em uwighhniillghatun. Akilghuughllagyan maaraghvinlegyaget kalluget tengngaagtaghtut.
Maaghraghvinlegyaget kalluget tengngaagtaghyata igaqnaqsaghanka sameng pillghit. Iwernga nagaqughaqa ma qilagmeng pilghii, “Aksaqiki maaghraghvinlegyaget kalluget sameng pillghit, igaqegpenaki!”
Taagken esghaghaqa yaqulek nekevghalghii kelliikunllu quutkunllu. Qilagmun nengugutii aghenqigneghet iiggeni,
akeqiiq Kiyaghneghem aatghakun kiyaghlleghhii quunperugllak kenlengunaan. Ellngangulghii ulimaghikaq qilagameng, nunameng, kelliineng, samengllu tamaghhaaneng taakunilngughneng. Yaqulek piiq, “Pilleghqaq kaatuq.
Iwernga maaghraghvinliitangita yaqulgem qalghighhnaqegkumigu qalghightaatni, taawa Kiyaghneghem apeghiighlleqaa uspeqilleni qayvighsimangilkenni sivunghani. Uspeqillgha ataasiiguq aapqaa qepghaghteminun uuknaliqistenun.”
Taagken nagaquqama mem qilagmeng aleghqughlaataghaanga, “Aglaghluten tuguki qelpalnguut iimgat igat iigganilnguut yaqulgem nekevghalghiim kelliikunllu quutkunllu.”
Yaqulegmun aglaghlunga tungsighanka imegngalghiit igaghhaat. Piinga, “Tuguluki neghiki; aqsaqughpeni qugaagllequt iwernga qaneghpeni muugallequt honey‑stun.”
Yaqulgem iigganeng tuguluki iimgat igaghhaat neghanka, imani qanemni muugatut honey‑stun. Iwernga tuufsaqenka aqsaquqa quwaagtaa.
Taagken piitnga, “Allameng uuknaliqutkepestaaghyaghqaqaten yulghutet, nunatalghutet, alaaghhiinaat ululghutet, umiilelghutetlu.”
Maalghuk UngipaghtekTaagken kitum ayaviilitaanga usputaasiqesqelluku. Enkaam kayagtaanga, “Usputaghyaghtughhu Kiyaghneghem Temple‑nga, aghqefigeklu, kesnaketenllu yuget maniguullghiit tawani.
Iwernga usputaghpenaan Kiyaghneghem Temple‑ngan court‑nga eslataanilnguq, qayughllak tuunegkaaguq Gentile‑enun. Tutmaasghaqnaqngwaat Agleghnalghii Neghllak forty two‑ghyagni tanqini.
Ungipaghtegka pilugugngalghiik sackcloth‑meng, aghtughyaghqaanghillelelleqagka uuknaliqesqellukek 1,260 aghneghnun.”
Maalghuk ungipaghtek maalghuguuk olive‑em uqfigek, maalghuguuklu kenelghutam tunemakek nekevghalghiik sivungani Atanghan nunam.
Enkaam kitum alngunak aqnighhnaqutkegkumikek, qaanghegkeneng kenghem aanluni tuququghlleqiik anguyagik. Kitumllu alngunak aqnighhnaqutkegkumikek taawa tuqusaghqaaghllequq.
Aghtughyaghqaanghillelguuk qilaga eslallugughnaniisqelluku uuknaliqellghegkegni. Aghtughyaghqaanghillelguuk meghet aawughtesqelluki. Aghtughyaghqaanghillelguuklu allaaghhiinaghneng ikfiqnalghiineng seghleliighllagneng, awen tawaten piiqellequk piyukelleghmegetun.
Apeghiiqayek ungipaneghmeng, asilighneghilngughmeng laawaaghmeng aanellequq teghikusalluuk. Pilluwaghlleqaak enkaam kayaalqegkumikek tuqulleqaak.
Kemegkwaaghik tamaanllequk tuumngani neghllagem, Atanghita qaquuraghvigani. Taana neghllak aatqeftuq Sodom‑emengllu Egypt‑mengllu qayughllak yugi Sodom‑eghmiistunllu Eygpt‑eghmiistunllu ayuqelghiit.
Yuget nunataghhaaneng, ramkeneng, allaaghhiinaghneng uluneng, nunatanengllu tagillequt esghaghnalukek kemegkwaaghik. Tawaten pillequt pingayunun aghneghnun avellelighluku, kitumunllu alngunak qungughtesnanighlleqagket.
Taakuk uuknaliqistek ikfiqestighllakaalghiik nunam yugitnun. Enkaam yuget quyaghllagllequt, tunquullequtlu tunusameng ilameggnun, apalluqluku tuqullghegkenun.
Iwernga kingungitneng pingayut aghneghet avellelighluku Kiyaghneghem aneghneni iteghtestekaa uuknaliqistegnun. Enkaam nekevyayek, qamaglluteng tamaakut esghaghlukek alingruughuteghllakat.
Taagken uuknaliqistek nagaqughaak iglagtupiglleghhii ma qilagmeng pilghii, “Mayughtek whavek!” Anguyagik esghapagumaluki mayughtuk qilagmun qilawaaghqun.
Tuunglighhaa seghlepestaaghllagem seghleliillghem alpagtuq, iwernga esghaghteggu pingayaa seghlepestaaghllagem seghleliillghem kaasaghtungestaghtuq.
Maaghraghvinliitanga QalghightaatemTaagken maaghraghvinliitangita yaqulgem qalghightaatni qalghightaa. Iglagtupiglluteng met qilagmi piit, “Ataneghpagullgha nunam ataneghpagulqaaghtaak Atanemtallu Christ‑anganllu, enkaam Ellnga igleghutillequq quunperugllak kenlengunaan!”
Taagken yuginaq estamat siipneqluku siivanlleghet aqumgalghiit umiilgusitgun aqumutamegteggun Kiyaghneghem sivungani, gginateng sekelluki manigughaat Kiyaghneq.
Pikaat:“Iyamsiqayugvikamken,Ataneq Kiyaghneq Aghtughyaghqaghhaanghilnguq,kiyaghlleghhii maaten, iiwlengllu kiyaghlleghhii! Tugumaan aghtughyaghqaanghitelleghllagen enkaam piinlightuten igleghutimun.
Nunam yugi sakriteghllagtut,iwernga maaten sakraalleghqan kaatuq.Tuqukat nanqigsaghqaaghtut.Akileghtughyaghqaaghtaten qepghaghteten uuknaliqistet,agleghnalghiit yugten,qamagllukillu siivakilghiit elpeneng,ukavanlenguutlu apeghseghutlu.Tuququlleghqan kaatuq tamaakunun tuququqaneng yugneng nunami.”
Taagken Kiyaghneghem Temple‑nga qilagmelnguq qelpateftuq. Tawani Temple‑ngani esghaghagka Ark‑ek Kiyaghneghem Covenant‑elghutakek. Taagken nighwaagpagtaghtuk, eftughtaghtuk, tengngaagtaghtuklu kallugek; nuna ufsuguteghllagtuq, kaftekragughteghllagaallu!
Aghnaankuk Dragon‑enkukTaagken qilagami sangwaa saghiighanapiglleghhii aliightuq liigikusighqaghput piyaghqamun: Aghnaq pilugugluni siqineghmeng, itegii tanqikun nekeglluteng, naasqumikun qaghpaluni qula maalghuk siipneqluku ighaleqetaaghneng.
Qumilguftuq, ighniyugem aqnighqelluku lliighaa, aanaqellghan taghnughhaam araghqaa.
Taagken qilagami sangwaa ilanga saghiighanapiglleghhii aliightuq liigikusighqaghput apeghiighnaqelghiimun: Taawa kavilnguq dragon‑eghllak, maaghraghvinlek naasqulek, qula sighunelek, enkaam qamaglluteng naasqwi qaghpalgututeftut.
Papegmineng saqipgutii nunamun pingayughqellghi qilagam ighaleqetaaghi. Taagken dragon‑a nekevegkaq manungakun aghnam neghnaluku taghnughhaa ighniighesnaqagu.
Aghnaq ighnenguq, igleghusaghqii qamagtengngwaaghluki nunam yugi iron‑meng anagutalighluni. Iwernga aghnam taghnughhaa akuqaghluku aglaataat Kiyaghneghmun, umiilgusigkenunllu aqumutagnun.
Aghnaq qimagtuq kilgaanun. Tamaani Kiyaghneghem yataaghqutkaqegkanga nekaghqameng, aflengaksaghqaqegkangat 1,260 aghneghet.
Taagken qilagmi pillugutut. Michael‑enkut yaqulkullghiit pilluwaghaat dragon‑a. Dragon‑enkut yaqulkullghiit pilluwaghiit Michael‑enkut yaqulkullghiit,
iwernga Michael‑enkut kayaalqaat dragon‑a. Enkaam dragon‑enkut yaqulkullghiit qilagmesaghqaananightut.
Qilagmeng miluutaat dragon‑eghllak. (Neghightaluk nemeghyaq aatgha Tughneghaq, nalighmeng Tughneghaq, puughqughtenga nunam yugan.) Miluutaat nunamun yaqulegtuumaan.
Taagken nagaqughaqa ma iglagtuluni qilagmeng pilghii,“Whaa kaasimaat Kiyaghneghem yugulighillgha,aghtughyaghqaanghillgha, ataneghpagullghallu,Christ‑anganllu aghtughyaghqaanghillgha.Salin Tughneghaq miluutellghilluku qilagmeng,aghneghtuumaan unugtuumaan anaggutnganiiqii ugpeqaalguteput Kiyaghneghmun.
Ugpeqaalgutemta kayaalqumaat aawakun Penniighaghaam,ungipaqelleghmegteggunllu Kiyaghneghem ipapighqellgha.Talwa tuquyaghngaaghmeng ayuqut Christ‑a apalluqluku.
Enkaam qamagllusi kiyaghlleghhiini qilagmi, quyateghllagtek!Iwernga seghleghwaaghunaqnguusi nunamelngughnillu kelliinilngughnillu!Tughneghaam ukigvikumiisi,sakriteghllaguuq qayughllak liisimakaa pilleghqiighusaghtughtuq.”
Dragon‑em liigiksamigu nunamun miluutelleni, malighqaghaa aghnaq ighnengegkaq.
Iwernga aghnaq tuunegkaat qawaagpagrugllagem yaqugkeneng tengaasqelluku kilgaanun. Tamaani paqniillequq nemeghyameng, aflengakelleqaatlu pingayut ayumiqullghet, aghvinlek tanqit ilalluki.
Taagken nemeghyam ughyuutaa meq kiiwestun ayuqelghii aghnaq maaqutesqelluku.
Iwernga nunam kayusiitaa aghnaq. Nunam agitaghulluku tuuftaa meghllak dragon‑em ughyuutkaa.
<sup>(17-18)</sup> Taagken dragon‑em ugumiyaguteghllagluku aghnaq, enkaam pilluwaghyaghtughii qamaglluki ilangi kingunghi. Tamaakunguut qaatkutngalghiit Kiyaghneghem qelghusiitnun, ataasiighmelnguutlu ipalleghmun apeghtuusaqegkaanun Jesus‑em.  Taagken dragon‑a nekevuq kelliim esnaakun.
Maalghuk TeghikusalluugekTaagken esghaghaqa teghikusalluuk aanelghii kelliimeng. Qulanguftut sighunghi, maaghraghvinlek naasqulek. Qamaglluteng sighunghi qaghpalgututeftut, tamaghhaghmeng naasqut igaqughvikngaftut ateghmeng seghlequulghiimeng Kiyaghneghmun.
Taana teghikusalluuk leopard‑esugnituq, itegii kayngem itegaatun ayuqelghiit, qaangha lion‑em qaanghatun ayuqelghii. Dragon‑em tuunaa teghikusalluuk aghtughyaghqaanghilleghmineng, umiilgusigmineng aqumutagneng, igleghutiyaghqaaghtestaallu ateni atuqluku.
Ataasiq naasqwa teghikusalluugem tuqutesugnitkaq kiitighluni, iwernga taana kiiyallgha maamegkaaftuq. Iingunaghhaghmeng nunam yugita saghiighayagulluku maligtaat teghikusalluuk.
Qamaglluteng yuget manigughaat dragon‑a qayughllak teghikusalluugmun tuunegkanga aghtughyaghqaanghilleni. Manigughaatlu teghikusalluuk, piit, “Kinangam teghikusalluugtun ayuqa? Kitumngam pilluwaghlleqagu?”
Taagken teghikusalluuk akuziyaghqaaghtuq. Aangaayugteghllagtuq, seghlepestaatunllu akuzitkaa Kiyaghneq. Aghtughyaghqaanghillenguq igleghutiyaghqaaluni 42‑nun tanqinun.
Piinlighaa seghlepestaatun akuzitkilleni Kiyaghneghmeng, aatghaneng, kiyaghfiganeng, tamaakunengllu kiyaghlleghhiineng qilagmi.
Qamaglluni nunami kiyaghlleghhiim manigughlleqaat teghikusalluuk. Iwernga tamaakut aatghit igaqngalghiit Igiitgun Unguvallghem manigughnaanghitaat. Kiyaghneghem igaqegkaqii aatghit nunangllallghilluni. Taakut igat pikii Penniighaghaam, yuget tuqutkiita.
“Nagatek, sigutelgukufsi:
Kina alngunak tuguyaghqaakumi, tugulleqaat. Kina alngunak tuqusaghqaakumi savigpagkun, tuqulleqaat savigpagkun. Taakuk whaten pisiiguk: Kiyaghneghem yugi nuqenneghtuyaghqaagutlu ugpeqillelguyaghqaagutlu.”
Taagken esghaghaqa ilanga teghikusalluuk nunameng aanelghii. Maalghugegneng sighunelguftuq penniighaghaam sighunghatun, akuziiqlu dragon‑etun.
Sivuliq teghikusalluuk tawanlluku tunglighhaan teghikusalluugem atuqaa qamaglluku aghtughyaghqaanghillgha. Taaggun aghtughyaghqaanghilleghqun maniguutestii qamaglluki nunam yugi sivulighmun teghikusalluugmun. (Kiiyallghan tuqutesugnitkaa, iwernga kiiyallgha maamegkaq.)
Tuunglighhaa teghikusalluuk allaaghlluwhaghtighllagaataghtuq, talwa qilagmeng nunamun keneq ukigtestaa yuget esghaamanghitni.
Tuunglighhaa teghikusalluuk aghtughyaghqaanghillenguq allaaghlluwaghtiyaghqaaluni tawantellghani sivuliim teghikusalluugem. Tamaagun allaaghlluwhaghtilleghteggun puughtii qamaglluki yuget kiyaghlleghhiit nunami. Qelghii yuget nangaghnenglliisqelluki quulviisqelluku sivuliq teghikusalluuk. (Taana tuqutkaayalghii savigpagkun iwernga unguvaqaq.)
Tuunglighhaa teghikusalluuk aghtughyaghqaanghillenguq aneghnengestiyaghqaaluni unguvalleghmeng nangaghneghanun teghikusalluugem. Enkaam nangaghneq akuziyaqlegughtuq. Taagken nangaghneghem qelghii yuget tuquqiisqelluki tamaakut maniguusunghilnguut ellminun.
Tuunglighhaan teghikusalluugem nalluniightiisqii number‑meng qamaglluki yuget aghenqigneghitgun iiggitgun nalighmeng qawiitgun. Tawaten qelghii aangwaaghughngaata, ukavansaghngaata, aklungiteghngaata, aklumaghngaata, qepghaghtelaaghunghiteghngaata, qepghaghtelaaghughngaata.
Kina alngunak tukfighiyaghqaanghituq nalighmeng akikiyaghqaanghituq wetkuqun nalluniillelgukumi. Taana nalluniilkutaq teghikusalluugem aatqaa nalighmeng aatghan number‑kaa.
Peghqinellelgem liigiknaaghaa una. Sumeghtaghalleghmikun liigikelleqaa sameng pisiitanga teghikusalluugem number‑nga. Taana number‑a yugmun aatghuuq, 666‑nguuq.
Penniighaghaqlu 144,000‑etlu YugetTaagken esghaghaqa taawa Penniighaghaq nekevghalghii Naayghami Zion‑mi. Ellnganituteftut 144,000 yuget, qagumegteggun igaqfikegkat aatghaneng, Atanganllu aatghaneng.
Nagaqughaqallu ma qilagmeng. Nagatkaaluni llangaqa qallangatun meghllaget, tengngaagatunllu kallugem. Nagatkaqa ma llangaqa harp‑estet aynganangallghiistun harp‑etgun ayuqelghii.
144,000 yuget nekevghatnguftut sivungani umiilgusim aqumutam, estamatlu unguvalghiit, elder‑etlu. Taakut yuget ilagaghaqeftut ilagaateghraghaghmeng. Kitum alngunak taana ilagaan liisaghqaqenghilkanga iwerngaqun 144,000 yuget. Ellnginguut Kiyaghneghem yugulikii qungangitneng nunam yuganeng.
Taakut yuget nukeggnaghqumangilnguugut aghnameng atuqilleghqun. Maligtaqaat Penniighaghaq navek alngunak pinghani. Kiyaghneghem yugulikaqii akulngitneng nunam yugan, tunusaqsuwhaaghuut Kiyaghneghmunllu Penniighaghaghmunllu.
Iqlengiqigatngwaaghtut. Apalliitut.
Pingayut YaqulgetTaagken esghaghaqa ilanga yaqulek tengaalghii quulvaghpani. Aapghii kenlengilnguut Pinilghiit Ungipat nunami kiyaghlleghhiinun, tamaghhiitnun nunataanilngughnun yugnun, ramkenun, ulunun, yugnunllu.
Iglagtupiglluni piiq, “Alikiteggu Kiyaghneq, usuqiteggu aangelleghllaga! Yugneng nanqigtilleghqaa kaatuuq. Manigughteggu ulimaghikaq qilagameng, nunameng, kelliineng, sengngulghiinengllu meghneng!”
Tuunglighhaan yaqulgem maligtaa sivuliq, whaten pimaghmi, “Naavumaaq! Babylon‑eghllak naavumaaq! Babylon‑em seghletun atuqillgha sex‑meng wine‑etun ayuquq. Wine‑mineng meghesqughii qamaglluki nunam yugi, enkaam ellngitallu seghletun sex atuqsagutaat. Enkaam tawaten pilleghmegteggun Kiyaghneghmun aghyuughteslequt.”
Pingayaak yaqulgem maligutuq sivuliignun. Iglagtupiglluni piiq, “Kitum alngunak maniguqumigu teghikusalluuk, nangaghneghallu, allgeghsimakumigullu nalluniilleq qagumikun nalighmeng iiggmikun
meghyaghqaqaa wine‑nga Kiyaghneghem sakraallghan. Taana wine‑a meliimangilnguq kuuvegkaq qayuusimun Kiyaghneghem sakraalqaa! Kina alngunak maniguutkaq taakugnun ikfiqeghllagyaghqaaguq keneghmillu, sulphur‑millu, sivungitni agleghnalghiitlu yaqulget, Penniighaghaamllu.
Kenghem ikfiqesteghllaglleqii, agepsaa mayughllequq quunperugllak kenlengunaan. Ikfiqnanighnaanghitut aghneghtuumaan unugtumaan, maniguutkaatmeggneng teghikusalluugmun, nangaghneghanun, nalluniiqaatmeggnengllu aatghaneng.”
Tamaakut qamaglluteng whaten pisiigut, Kiyaghneghem yugi nuqenneghtupestaaghyaghqaagut. Tamaakunguut qaatkutngalghiit Kiyaghneghem qelghusaanun, ataasiighmellutengllu Jesus‑mun.
Taagken nagaqughaqa qilagmeng ma pilghii, “Igaqigu una: Whaken kenlekluku quyasaghqaagut tuquyaghqat qepghaasimaluku Ataneq!”Taghneghak piik, “Quyanapestaaghtut! Meghnaalillequt ughleghiilleghmeggneng, yuget neqamikelleqiit aneghneghqillghit.”
Nunameng UnatalleqTaagken esghaghaqa taawa qatelghii qilawaaq, qilawaghqun aqumgaftuq llangaqa ighnegha yugem. Naasqumikun gold‑meng qaghpalguftuq, tugumiiqeftaallu ipelghii pakregmelnguq savik.
Taagken ilanga yaqulek aanuq Temple‑meng. Akilghuughllagaa aqumgalghii qilagwaaghmi, “Pakregmelnguq savigen atuqluku unataa, qayughllak unatalleghqaq kaatuq, nunam piitestekaa unataghyaghqaaghtengnguuq!”
Enkaam qilawaaghmi aqumgalghiim pakregmelnguq savini unataasiqaa nunamun.
Taagken ilanga yaqulek aanuq Temple‑meng qilagmi, ellngallu ipelghiimeng pakregmelngughmeng savilguftuq.
Taagken ilanga yaqulek aanuq aghqefigegneng aflengakistenga kenghan aghqefigem. Akilghuughllagaa yaqulek ipelghiimeng pakregmelngughmeng savilek, “Savigpeneng kepughqi grapes‑et nunam vine‑nganeng, qayughllak grapes‑et qigumaat!”
Grapes‑mun qageghquusik eslataanilnguuk neghllagem. Grapes‑et qageghqughyalghiimeng aawk maaquq qageghquusineng 180 miles tagtalkelluku, 5 feet uusqaghtulkelluku.
Moses‑enkuk Penniighaghaankuk IlagaatngakTaagken qilagami aliightuq sangwaa saghiighanapiglleghhii liisimakusighqaghput piyaghqamun. Taawa maaghraghvinlek yaqulget, tagitilghiit maaghraghvinlegneng seghleliilleghllagneng. Taakut seghleliilleghllaget taaqniitkeftii Kiyaghneghem sakraalleghllagan.
Taagken esghaghaqa kelliisugnilnguq meghraakegtaq siqinwaaghestun, akumngalghii keneghmeng. Esghaghankallu kayaalqiikat teghikusalluugmeng, nangaghneghaneng, aatghanllu number‑nganeng. Nekevghatnguftut saaghwaghni kelliim, harp‑elightuulluteng Kiyaghneghem tuunegkiitneng ellngitnun.
Ilagaghaqeftut ilagaatanganeng Moses‑em, (Kiyaghneghem qepghaghtenga), ilagaatanganengllu Penniighaghaam:“Kaay, Ataneq Kiyaghneq Aghtughyaghqaghhaanghiteghllak,qepghalleghten seghleghllaguut, allaaghlluwhaghllaguut!Kaay, umiilgat nunam yugita,elpek salleghten elqughutngaatlu ipanguutlu!
Ataneq, qamagtengngwaaghluteng yuget alikelleqaaten,quulvaghlleqaatlu aatghen!Ellnginaaguten agleghnalghii!Qamagtengngwaaghluteng nunatat manigughyaghtughlleqaaten,qayughllak liisimakegkangat nanqigtilleghten elqughutngalghiit!”
Kinguliit Maaghraghvinlek SeghleliilleghllagetTaam kingunganeng esghaghaqa qilagmi qelpeghtekangat Temple‑a. (Agleghnalleghpigaaguq Na, ellngan yugita liisimakusiqaat Kiyaghneq tawanniluku.)
Taagken maaghraghvinlek yaqulget aanleghaatut Temple‑meng kelqelluteng maaghraghvinlegneng seghleliilleghllagneng. Tamaghhaghmeng atkuyaaghulluteng qateghrakegtameng nighulghiimeng, sakimagmegteggun gold‑meng tafsiluteng.
Taagken ataasim unguvalghiim estamaneng taakuneng, gold‑meng sagneliqughii maaghraghvinlek yaqulget. Taakut sagneghet imighngaat sakraalleghllaaganeng Kiyaghneghem, kiyaghlleghhii quunperugllak kenlengunaan.
Temple‑em ilunga agepsughqaagaa Kiyaghneghem nighughqellghanengllu, aghtughyaghqaanghillghanengllu. Kina alngunak iteghnaanghituq Temple‑mun kenlanga maaghraghvinlek seghleliilleghllaget kenletghuutellghitnun, tagitkiit maaghraghvinlek yaqulget.
Sagneghet Imaqelghiit Kiyaghneghem SakritelleghllaganengTaagken Temple‑meng nagaqughaqa iglagtulghii ma, ungipaaskangi maaghraghvinlek yaqulget, “Kuuvyaghtughteki nunamun maaghraghvinlek sagneghet Kiyaghneghem sakraalleghllagi!”
Enkaam sivuliim yaqulgem sagneni kuuvyaghtughaa nunamun. Taagken seghlepestaaghllaget aqnighnapiglleghhiit pupiget piitquutut nalluniillengegkanun teghikusalluugmeng. Tamaakunguut maniguutkat nangaghneghanun.
Tuunglighhaan yaqulgem sagneni kuuvaa kelliinun. Taagken kellii aawatun tuqukam yugem lliighluni, enkaam qamaglluteng unguvalghiit kelliini tuqulaghaatut.
Pingayiitangita yaqulgem sagneni kuuvaa kiigwnunllu, sengngununllu meghnun enkaam aawughquutut.
Nagaqughaqa igleghutilghii meghneng yaqulek pilghii,“Kaay, Agleghnalghii Kiyaghneq,elpenguuq maaten kiyaghlleghhii,elpenguuq quunpeng kiyaghlleghhii!Nanqigtilleghtenllu aghyuughilleghtenllu elqughutngaat.
Yuget tuququqaqiit yugten, uuknaliqistetenllu,enkaam meghyaghqalitaten aawmeng.Tawaten aghyuughyaghqaaluteng ellmeggneng allgeghtekaqaat!”
Taagken nagaqughaqa aghqefigegneng ma pilghii,“Aa‑a Ataneq, Kiyaghneq Aghtughyaghqaanghilnguq!Ipanguutlu elqughutngaatlu nanqigtilleghqaghten!”
Estamiitangita yaqulgem saghneni kuuvaa siqineghqun enkaam Kiyaghneghem siqinghem kenghanun paneghtestii yuget.
Siqinghem uguqnaghllagan paneghtestii yuget. Enkaam sanguughteghllagaat aatgha Kiyaghneghem, igleghutistengutanganeng tamaavek seghleliilleghllagnun. Avuteghqenghitutlu, usuqenghitaatlu Kiyaghneghem aangelleghllaga.
Tallimiitangita yaqulgem sagneni kuuvaa teghikusalluugem umiilgusiin aqumutagkenkun, enkaam ataneghpagullgha mamleghqwaagaa. Yuget ikfiqem uluteng amqeghqughiit.
Sanguughteghllagaat Kiyaghnegha qilagem apalluqluku aqnighqelleghmeggnengllu pupigtaalleghmeggnengllu. Avuteghqenghitutlu seghletun pilleghmeggneng.
Aghvinliitangita yaqulgem sagneni kuuvaa kiiwllagegnun Euphrates‑egnun. Kiiwek pateghtuk yataaghqunnaluki tuumkaghqameng umiilget tagilghiit asivaghmeng.
Taagken esghaghanka pingayut nukeggnalghiit tughneghaat frog‑esugnilnguut. Aanut qaanghitneng dragon‑em, teghikusalluugem, uuknaliqistesighwaaghemllu.
Taakut tughneghaat allaaghlluwhaghtikayuguftut. Aghulaqut umiilgitnun nunataghhaan tamaghhaan qerngughhnaluki pilluwamun aghneghllagani Kiyaghneghem Aghtughyaghqaghhaanghilnguum.
Ataneq piiq, “Nagataghtek! Taginguunga teglegniightetun! Quyanaghtuq teghhumalghii, aatkani piiftengngwaaghluki ayuqegkangi. Enkaam igleghhnaanghituq amsikaghmi, kayngusaghaannaanghituqlu tesqagani yuget esghaqumegteggu!”
Taagken tughneghaat qerngughtiit umiilget Armageddon‑mun. Tawaten Hebrew‑ghmiistun atillgha ayuquq.
Taagken maaghraghvinliitangita yaqulgem sagneni kuuvaa eslakun. Temple‑mi umiilgusigneng aqumutaghllagegneng iglagtupiglluni ma piiq, “Apeghiightuq!”
Taawa nighwaagpagtaghtuq, tengngaagtaghtuq, kallituq, nunallu ufsuguteghllagtuq. Taana nunam ufsugutelleghllaga seghlelleghpigaaguq Kiyaghneghem yungllaghyuggallghaneng.
Neghllak pelleghtuq pingayughqelluni. Nunatlu neghllagit qamagtengngwaaghluteng naavuutut. Kiyaghneghem neqamikii Babylon‑eghllagem seghleghqellghi. Enkaam meghestaa wine‑a qayuusimelnguq sakritelleghllagmineng imaqelghii.
Qamaglluteng qiighqat aviighuquutut, qamagllutengllu naayghat kaavuutut.
Aghnaqlu TeghikusalluukluTaagken yaqulget maaghraghvinlegneng sagnelget, taakuneng ataasim takulunga piinga, “Tagi, kelguviknaqamken aghyuulleghqaaneng apeghseghuum aghnam yugusimineng akikikayugem, aqumgalghii meghllagteggun.
Nunam umiilgi seghleghqaqut atuqaqluku aghnaq. Seghleghet atuqistillghi wine‑etun ayuqut, enkaam nunam yugi suumaqut meneghmegteggu wine‑nga.”
Taagken yaqulgem Taghneghagnekun aglaataanga kilgaanun. Tawani esghaghaqa aghnaq aqumgalghii kavirrakegtakun teghikusalluugkun. Teghikusalluuk igaqughvikngaftuq uzimun sanguughtusineng ateghneng Kiyaghneghmun. Maaghraghvinlek naasqulguftuq, quulnguftutlu sighunghi.
Aghnaq pilugugngaftuq esneyaaghmengllu kavirrakegtamengllu, enkaam ullngaqluni gold‑meng, akitughllagmeng uyghagmeng, pearl‑mengllu. Tugumiiqeftaa gold‑a qayuusiq esleqngalghii seghleghnalghiineng kiyaghtaalleghneng, nukeggnalghiinengllu sex‑kun seghleghqellghaneng.
Qawaani igaqngaftuq ateq qayvighsimangilnguq whaten pisiq,
Esghaghaqa aghnaq suumelghii aawitneng Kiyaghneghem yugita, aawitnengllu tuququqat qayughllak ataasiighmelnguut Jesus‑mun.Esghaghluku aghnaq saghiighayugllagtunga.
Iwernga yaqulgem piinga, “Sangavek saghiighayugsin? Ungipaannaqamken qayvighsimangilngughmeng sameng pisiitkek aghnaankuk, teghikusalluugenkuk. Taana teghikusalluuk igleghutilghii aghnameng, naasqulguuq maaghraghvinlek, sighunelguuqlu qula.
Teghikusalluuk esghaqan unguvayalghiinguuq, Iwernga tuqukaaguq. Mayughllequq Saamnangilngughmeng Laagwaaghmeng naafqellengnaluni. Yulguuq nunami aatghit igaqellghilnguut Igiitgun Unguvallghem nuna piinlillghilluku. Tamaakut yuget esghaqumegteggu teghikusalluuk saghiighayugllequt qayughllak unguvayalghii, tuqukaq iwernga tagiyaghqaq.
“Sumeghtaghayuqam liigikelleqaa una: Maaghraghvinlek naasqut maaghraghvinleguut qemit aghnam aqumgavigi.
Taakut naasqut maaghraghvinleguutlu umiilget. Tallimat tuqukaagut, ataasiq igleghutinguuq, enkaam ataasiq salin tagingigatuq. Tagikumi igleghutiyaghqaaguq natengiighhaq.
Teghikusalluuk unguvayalghii iwernga tuqukaq, pingayuneng ingluliitnguuq umiilek. Taana pingayuneng ingluliita umiilek ilakaat sivuliit maaghraghvinlek umiilget, naafqellengyaghtuuguq.
“Esghaqaghten qula sighunghet, qulanguut umiilget salin igleghutingigatut. Iwernga aghtughyaghqaanghillengellequt igleghutiyaghqaaluteng ataasiq aflu maligulluteng teghikusalluugmun.
Taakut ataasiq umyugaqluku tuunelleqiit teghikusalluugmun aghtughyaghqaanghilletengllu pilleghqatengllu.
Enkaam pilluwaghlleqaat Penniighaghaq. Iwernga Penniighaghaam kayaalqelleqii qayughllak Atanqegkangat atanghet, Umiilkegkangatlu umiilget. Penniighaghaghmelnguut tuqluqaagut, nakmikegkaagut, ataasiighmelnguugutlu.”
Taagken yaqulgem piinga, “Esghaghaten meghet aghnam yugusimineng akikikayugem aqumgavigi. Taakut meghet yulghuteghllaguut nunataghhaaneng tamaghhaaneng pinguut, ulukelghiit allaaghhiinaghmeng.
Esghaqaghpek qula sighunghet, teghikusalluugemllu, ugumiilleqaat aghnaq yugusimineng akikikayuk. Saqraggiighulluku, amsiqaghqelluku, kemga neghluku, taagken siipnegha kumaghlleqaat.
Taakut qula sighunghet tawaten pikaagut qayughllak Kiyaghneghem ellngitnun atuqestekaqaa piyukelleni. Angeghqumatkaagutlu tuunaluki ataneghpagulleteng teghikusalluugmun. Tawaten pikaagut kenlanga Kiyaghneghem piyukellgha apeghiillghanun.
Taana aghnaq esghaqan neghllaguuq igleghutilghii umiilgitneng nunat.”
Babylon‑em NaafqellghaTaam kingunganeng esghaghaqa ilanga yaqulek qilagmeng ukilghii. Aghtughyaghqaanghillelegllaguftuq, nighughqelleghmineng iingunaghhaan nuna nighugtaa.
Akilghuughllagtuq,“Naavumaaq! Naavumaaq Babylon‑eghllak!Nekaaghsimaat tughneghaat,nukeggnalghiit tughneghaat,ukmanginneghilnguut kusgenalghiit qawaaget.
Babylon‑em seghletun atuqillgha sex‑meng wine‑etun ayuquq,nunataghhan tamaghhaan meghaa.Nunam umiilgita atuqaqaat,nunamllu akilpegaghtengita aklungighisiqngwaat nuqetusaghqaanghilngughqun sex‑kun atuqiyullghakun.”
Taagken nagaqughaqa ilanga ma qilagmeng pilghii,“Yumni, aanleghaatek Babylon‑meng!Ilategpenasi seghleghqellghanun aghyuullengnayukafsi ellnganun maligullusi.
Seghleghqellghi mayughteghllagngaat uusqaghtutkaghmeng qilagtun,Kiyaghneghem neqamikii seghleghqellghi.
Seghletun piteggu Babylon katam ellngan seghletun pillghatun.Malghughqelluku seghletun pillgha piteggu.Qayuusiikun kuuviteggu wine‑a iknaqetulnga malghughqengngaan ellngan atuqaqegkanganeng.
Ellmineng usuqeghllagaquq,aklungighllanillu atuqaqaa samun alngunak piyukegkaminun.Enkaam ikfiqesteghllagteggullu qivghusteghllagteggullu atunekiitesluku qaghyalleghllaganun.Ellmineng piiquq,‘Queen‑nguunga aqumgalghii umiilgusimkun.Ugingighaanghitunga enkaam qivghunaanghitngwaaghtunga!’
Tamaaken apalluqluku aghneghhiinaghmi kaalleqaa tuqullghem,qivghullghem, neqangisagllagem.Taagken kenghem paneghlleqaa qayughllak aghyuughistenga,Ataneq Kiyaghneq, aghtughyaghqaanghiteghllagtuq.”
Nunam umiilgi ilatkat atuqillghanunllu qiliighyullghanunllu, esghaqumegteggu agepsaa panellghan qiyakelleqaat, iglagtupigllutengllu qiyakeghllaglleqaat.
Uyavanlluteng nekevellequt qayughllak alingelghiit ellmengllu ilannayukameng ikfiqellghanun. Pillequt,“Seghleghhaghmeng! Seghleghhaghmeng elpek aangeghllak aghtiigalnguq neghllak, Babylon!Aghyuullenguten ataasighhaghmi aflumi!”
Nunam akilpegaghtengita qiyaaghwaatkaat qivghughllagumaghmeng, qayughllak kitum alngunak tukfighnaniqangit saghyangit.
Akikaqsaqangitlu cinnamon‑et, spice‑et, incense‑et, myrrh‑et, frankincense‑et; wine‑et, olive‑em mesiighi; avlawat, wheat‑et; cattle‑et, penniighet, kuunit, wagon‑et; talwa yuget akikaqsaqangit qepghaghtelaaghuluki.
Akilpegaghtet Babylon pilleqaat, “Qamaglluteng pinilghiit allgeghsukeghllakaghten aviighutut. Qamagllutengllu aklungighllagten qelmeghllaget aviighutut, allamengllu allgeghsaghqaananighaten!”
Akilpegaghtet aklungighikat akikiluteng Babylon‑mun, nekevghallequt uyavanlluteng qayughllak alingelghiit ilannayukameng ikfiqellghanun. Qiyallequt qivghughllagumaghmeng,
whatenllu pillequt,“‘Seghleghwaaghuuq! Seghleghwaaghuuq neghllak!Aatkayuguyaghtuq linen‑meng, esneyaaghmeng,kavirrakegtamengllu, ullngaqegkayuguyaghtuqlu gold‑meng,akitughllagmeng uyghagmeng, pearl‑mengllu!
Ataasimi aflumi aklungighllagiitaa!’“Qamaglluteng angyalget, yugit, passenger‑ngit, akilpegaghtetlu igleghakayuget angyaghpagteggun allgeghunnaluteng kiyaghusighqameggneng, angyaghpagit aghuliiqat uyavanlluteng Babylon‑meng kumaghaqngan.
Esghaghluku agepsaa kumallghan, akilghuugut, ‘Alla neghllagituq whatelngughmeng!’
Naasquteng pagulalightughiit qiyatkelluku, qivghutkelluku akilghuugut,‘Seghleghwaaghuuq! Seghleghwaaghuuq neghllak!Aklungighllaganeng qamaglluteng angyaghpalget aklungighikayuguyaghtut!Iwernga ataasimi aflumi aklungighllagiitaa!’”
Taagken qilagmeng kina piiq,“Kaay qilagmelngughni, quyakiteggu qayughllak Kiyaghneghem naafqaa Babylon!Quyatek Kiyaghneghem yugitni,apostle‑eni, uuknaliqistenillu!Kiyaghneghem aghyuughaa qayughllak seghletun pikaqegkangisi!”
Taagken iknaqeghllalghiim yaqulgem kevgaa uyghagrugllak, grain‑mun kagimtisistun ayuqelghii. Miluutaa kellimun, whaten pimaghmi,“Tawateghpigaq neghllak Babylon,Kiyaghneghem miluuteghllaglleqaa asitmun enkaam allamengllu esghaghnaanghitaat.
Kitum alngunak nagaqughnaanghitii harp‑esteten,pillgughikat aynganangasteten,flute‑esteten, qalghightaghtetenllu!Qamaglluteng pillgughikat qepghaghteten aviighusaghqaagut,grain‑meng kagimtesteten allallu nagaqughnaanghitiit!
Kenelghutam nighuga kuukgunnaanighnaquq elpeni.Mengik nulightughnaqelghiimllu ugiighnaqelghiimllu nagaqughnanighnaquk elpeni.Akilpegaghteten aghtiigatngwaaghyaghtut nunataghhaani tamaghhaani.Alignaghtaalleghpegun puughquqaqaten qamagtengngwaaghluki nunam yugi!
Babylon‑mi taawa aawit uuknaliqistet,Kiyaghneghem yugi, qamagllutengllu tuqutkat nunami.”
Kingunganeng iknaqeghllalghiim yaqulgem akuzillghan, qilagmi nagaqughanka yulghuteghllaget akilghuulghiit,“Hallelujah!Yugulilleq, quulvalleq, aghtughyaghqaanghilleqlu Kiyaghnemta pikii!
Ellngan nanqigtillghi ipanguut, elqughutngaat!Ellngan aghyuuqaqaa apeghseghuq aghnaq yugusimineng akikikayuk qayughllak nunam yugi seghletun pistekangi sex‑kun atuqestaqluni.Kiyaghneghem akitkaqaa qayughllak qepghaghtengi tuququghtestekangi.”
Yulghuteghllaget akilghuulaataghtut,“Hallelujah!Neghllagem kumalghiim agepsaa mayuuguq quunperugllak kenlengunaan!”
Taagken yuginaq estamat siipneqluki elder‑et, estamatlu unguvalghiit niinghuquulluteng manigughaat Kiyaghneq, aqumgalghii umiilgusigmikun. Pikaat,“Amen! Hallelujah!”
Penniighaghaam Nengughtellghan NeqenghaghqellghaTaagken umiilgusigneng aqumutaghllagegneng ma whaten piiq,“Usuqiteggu Kiyaghneghput,qamagllusi qepghaghtengani alikilghiini ellnganeng,ukavanlengughnillu aangwaaghnillu!”
Taagken nagaqughanka llangaqa mengit yulghuteghllaget. Nagatkaaluteng suksugistun tevlughteghllalghiit meghet, kallugemllu tengngaagtallghatun ayuqluteng. Akilghuugut,“Hallelujah!Ataneq Kiyaghneghput, Aghtughyaghqaghhaanghilnguq igleghutiiq!
Quyatelta, elngaatall quyaghllageltallu usuqelteggullu!Penniighaghaam nengughtelleghqaa kaatuq,nuliighqaallu yataaghqumaaq.
Kiyaghneghem aasightuumaa ugiighnaqelghii pinighrakegtameng qatelghiimeng linen‑meng.”(“Linen‑a” whaten pisiiguq, elqughutngalghiit aneghneghqillghet Kiyaghneghem yugita piiqegkangit.)
Taagken yaqulgem piinga, “Una igaqigu: Penniighaghaam nengughtellghan neqenghaghqellghanun neghyaghtiisqegkat quyastekaagut.” Whatenllu piinga, “Ukut ipanguut akuzitangi Kiyaghneghem.”
Taagken niinghutunga yaqulgem itegaakun manigughnaluku, iwernga piinga, “Tawaten pigpenang! Manigughhu Kiyaghneq! Qepghaataqaqa Kiyaghneq elpetun, ugpeqaalgutegpetunllu. Ellnginguut ataasiighmelnguut ipalleghmun Jesus‑em apeghtuusaqegkaanun. Ipalleq Jesus‑em apeghtuusaqegkaa taananguuq ipalleq Kiyaghneghem Taghneghagkenka uuknaliqistenun ungipaqestekaa.”
Igleghastenga Qatelghiim KuunimTaagken esghaghaqa qilak qelpelghii, taawa qatelghii kuuni! Kuunikun igleghlleghhiim aatgha “Ataasiighmelnguq, Ipapik”. Elqughutngaat nanqigtillghi, pilluwaqangillu anguyani.
Iiskek kumaghullghatun kenghem ayuqlutek, naasqumikun qaghpalghutelguftuq. Aatgha ellngakun igaqngaftuq kitum alngunak nallukegkanga iwerngaqun ellnginaan.
Atkuyaaghek atukek neptekaaftuk aawkun. Aatqeftaa, “Kiyaghneghem Akuzitanga”.
Qilagmeng pilluwaghtengita maligsaaghaat uuglluteng qatelghiitgun kuunitgun, atkuyaaghluteng iqangilngughmeng qatelghiimeng linen‑meng.
Qaanghaneng aanuq ipelghii savigpak, taaggun qamagtengngwaaghluki nakumiit kayaalqughlleqii. Igleghulleqii iron‑meng anagutalighluni. Taagken tutmaghlleqii anguyani katam yuget tutmaghaqellghistun grapes‑et qageghquusignilnguut. Taana tutmalleq sakraalleghllakaa Kiyaghneghem Aghtughyaghqaghhaanghilnguum.
Atkuyaaghakunllu qugtuqaakunllu igaqngaftuq ateq whaten; <font size=-1>Umiilga umiilget, Atangha atanghet.</font>
Taagken esghaghaqa yaqulek nekevghalghii siqineghqun. Qamaglluki qawaalghutet quulvani tengaalghiit iglagtupiglluni pii, “Tagilaghaallusi qerngughutek Kiyaghneghem neqenghaghqelleghllaganun!
Taagken esghaghanka teghikusalluuklu, nunamllu umiilgi, pilluwaghtekullghiit qerngughutut pilluwaghnaluku igleghlleghhii kuunikun, pilluwaghtengillu.
Tugwaagket teghikusalluugenkuk, uuknaliqistesighwaaghenkuk allaaghlluwaghtiighaataqaq tawanlluku teghikusalluuk. (Allaaghlluwaghtiiqelleghmikun puughquqii nalluniillengegkat teghikusalluugmeng, maniguqaatlu nangaghnegha.) Teghikusalluugenkuk, uuknaliqistesighwaaghenkuk unguvaagkenka miluutaak naayvam kenghanun kumaghulghiimun sulphur‑meng.
Pilluwaghtengik kuunikun igleghlleghhiim tuququghii savigpagkun qaneghmineng aanegkakun. Taagken qamaglluteng qawaaget neghiit kemegkwaaghit kepsuqiinalleghmeggnun.
Thousand AyumiqullghetTaagken esghaghaqa yaqulek qilagmeng ukilghii tugumiiqluni key‑nganeng Saamnangilnguum Laawaaghem, qiipraghuteghllagnengllu.
Kayaalqelluku dragon‑a tuwaa. (Dragon‑a taananguuq ayumightaq nemeghyaq, aatgha Tughneghaq, Tughneghaq.) Taagken yaqulgem asighqaa qiipraghutneng thousand ayumiqulleghnun.
Miluulluku Laawaaghmun, taagken amigmeng uumgulluku maghqatutkaa seal‑eluku. Enkaam Dragon‑em puughsaghqaananighii yuget kenlanga thousand ayumiqullghet alpallghitnun. Alpakata itemutaghlleqaat.
Taagken esghaghanka umiilgusit aqumutat, aqumgalghiitlu taakutgun. Kiyaghneghem nanqigtiyaghqaaghtestekii yugneng. Eshaghankallu unguvasiit tamaakut naasqwightuqiit apalluqluku Jesus. Ungipaqegkaqegkangat ipalleq Jesus‑em qayvighqegkaa, akuzitangillu Kiyaghneghem. Taakut maniguusimangitut teghikusalluugmun, nalighmeng nangaghneghanun. Talwa qagumegteggun, nalighmeng iiggmegteggun allgeghtellghitaat nalluniilkutaa teghikusalluugem. Unguvaghtuulluteng igleghutilgusighaat Christ‑a thousand ayumiqulleghnun.
Taana sivuliiguq unguvaghqulleq. (Ilangi tamaakut tuqukat unguvaghtuunnaanghitut kenlanga thousand ayumiqullghet alpallghitnun.)
Tamaakut Kiyaghneghem unguvaghtekii unguvaghtuusuwhaalleghmi quyastekaagutlu agleghnaghtutlu. Tuqunaanghitut tuunglighhaani tuqullghem. Iwernga priest‑ngunaqnguut Kiyaghneghmunllu Christ‑amunllu. Igleghutilgusighlleqaatlu Christ‑a thousand ayumiqulleghni.
Kiyaghneghem Kayaalqegkanga TughneghaqThousand ayumiqullghet alpakata, Tughneghaq anusimingllaghviganeng itemusaghqaaguq.
Enkaam aanluni puughqughlleqii nunatat mingitngalghiit nunataghhaani tamaghhaani. Tamaakut nunatat aatqiit Gog‑enkuk Magog‑enkuk. Yugik uglaghllagtut qenaavzeghaatun esnem. Taagken Tughneghaam qerngughlleqii pilluwamun.
Tughneghaam pilluwaghtengi iqelmun mingilluteng igleghllequt nunakun. Kaalluteng kangllulleqagket nunaaqlu Kiyaghneghem yugita nayaat, neghllaklu Kiyaghneghem piniqegkaa. Taagken qilagmeng Kiyaghneghem keneq ukigtesluku paneghtekii pilluwaghtet.
Taagken Tughneghaq puughtikaq nunataneng, Kiyaghneghem yaqulgita miluulleqaat naayvamun kumaghulghii sulphur‑meng. Tawavek miluutkaqegkegket teghikusalluugenkuk, uuknaliqistesighwaaghenkuk. Tawani ikfiqeghllagllequt aghneghtuumaan unugtuumaan quunperugllak kenlengunaan.
Kinguliq NanqigtilleqTaagken esghaghaqa Kiyaghneq aqumgalghii qatelghiignekun umiilgusignekun aqumutaghllagegnekun. Nunallu qilagallu qimaaguutuk Kiyaghneghem tawantellghaneng, allallu esghaghyaghqaagpenatek.
Esghaghankallu tuqulaghaatkat, ukaliiwaqlutengllu aangwaaghwaaqlutengllu ayuqelghiit. Nekevghatnguftut sivungani umiilgusim aqumutaghllagem. Taagken igat qelpeghtiit, Igii Unguvallghem, igaqughvikegkat aatghitneng tamaakut unguvayaghqat quunperugllak. Ilangillu igalghutet qelpeghtiit igaqughvikegkat tuqukat kiyaghtaallghitneng ayuqelghiit. Kiyaghneghem nanqigtii atuqluki igaquqat igatgun.
Taagken kelliim tuqumasliini pegtii. Tuqullghemllu Hades‑emllu tuqumasliitek pegtiik. Qamagtengngwaaghluki Kiyaghneghem nanqigtii kiyaghtaallghistun.
Taagken Tuqulleqlu Hades‑lu miluutagket naayvam kenghanun. Naayvam kengha tuungliqaa tuqullghem.
Kitum alngunak aatgha igaqumangilkan Igaani Unguvallghem, miluutkaat naayvam kenghanun.
Qilagraghaqlu NunaghraghaqluTaagken esghaghagka qilagraghaqlu nunaghraghaqlu. Qilaksuwhaaghiisimaaq, nunaksuwhaaghiisimaaq, kelliingiitkaaguqlu.
Esghaghaqallu Agleghnalghii Neghllak, Jerusalem‑eghraghaq, ukilghii Kiyaghneghmeng qilagmelngughmeng. Neghllak yataaghqelluni ugiighnaqelghiim ullngaqellghatun ugiminun.
Nagaqughaqa ma iglagtupiglleghhii umiilgusigneng aqumutagneng pilghii, “Esghaqaghhuqun, Kiyaghneghem kiyaghfiga yugnituq! Kiyaghfikelleqii enkaam ellngit yukelleqii. Kiyaghneq ellnga katam ellngitnillequq enkaam ellnga Kiyaghneqelleqaat.
Quningighlleqii qamaglluki. Tuqungiilleqaa, qivghungiilleqaa, qiyangiilleqaa, talwa aqnighqengngiilleqaa qayughllak tamaakut atuqsaqangit atuqnanighlleqiit.”
Taagken umiilgusignilnguq aqumutagni piiq, “Esghaqaghqiqun, ulimaaqanka sangwaat qamagtengngwaaghluki nutaghaaluki!” Whatenllu piiq, “Igaqiki tamaakut aapqanka elpenun qayughllak tamaakut akuzitet ipanguut, ugpeqsaghqaagutlu.”
Piingallu, “Apeghiightuq! Whanga Alpha‑nguunga Omega‑nguunga, whanga piinleghuunga kenlenguunga. Kina alngunak meqsulghii, akingunaan meghsilleqaqa sengngulghiimeng unguvallengestikayugmeng meghmeng.
Kitum alngunak kayaalqiilghiim allgeghlleqii tamaakut whangamneng. Kiyaghneqelleqaatnga enkaam ellngit avaqutaqelleqanka.
Iwernga tamaakut quyughtalghiit, ugpeqillghilnguut, seghlelleghpigaghneng seghleghqelghiit, yugtaghtet, nengughtegpenateng atuqullghiit, alignalghiit, maniguutkayuget kiyaghnengllaqanun, qamagllutengllu iqlengalghiit, nekaghqaat naayvaaguq kumaghulghii keneghmengllu sulphur‑mengllu. Taananguuq tuunglii tuqullghem.”
Jerusalem‑eghraghaqTaagken yaqulget maaghraghvinlegneng sagnelget esleqngalghiineng kingulighneng seghleliilleghllagneng, ataasim taakuneng takwaanga. Piinga, “Tagi, kelguviknaqamken Ugiighnaqelghiimeng, nuliighqaa Penniighaghaam.”
Kiyaghneghem Taghneghagkenkun yaqulgem tugulunga aglaataanga uusqalleghpigaanun naaygham. Tawani kelgutaa Jerusalem, Agleghnalghii Neghllak ukilghii Kiyaghneghmeng qilagmelngughmeng.
Kuukgutngaghmi Kiyaghneghem nighughqellghaneng. Neghllak kuukgutuq akitughllalghiitun uyghagtun, jasper‑etun, meghraakegtutkaghmi crystal‑etun.
Mingllutanga neghllagem qula maalghuk siipneqluku amigllalek, pingayut asivaghmi, pingayut aywaani, pingayut ikevaghmi, pingayut pakfallami.
Neghllagem mingllutanga tunemiqaaftuq qula maalghuk siipneqluku uyghagneng. Ataasikaghtaghmeng uyghaget igaqfikngaftut ateghmeng qula maalghuk siipneqluku apostle‑nganeng Penniighaghaam.
Yaqulek aleghqughteka gold‑meng usputalguftuq usputaghnaluku neghllak, amigllagillu mingllutangallu.
Neghllak ulluviighrakegteftuq tagtalnga, pateghtulngatun ayuqeftuq. Yaqulgem neghllak usputaghyaqminigu: 1,500 miles tagtalkeftaa, pateghtulkeftaa, uusqaghtulkeftaallu.
Mingllutangallu usputaghyaqminigu, 216 feet‑nguftuq uusqaghtulnga. Yaqulgem usputallghatun ayuqeftuq yugem usputallgha.
Mingllutanga ulimaaghuftuq jasper‑meng. Neghllak ulimaaghuftuq gold‑eperegwaaghmeng. Gold‑a meghraakegtepiglleghhii siqinwhaaghtun.
Neghllagem mingllutangan tunemii pinighnaaqusighluteng allaaghhiinaghneng akitughllagneng uyghagneng. Sivuliq jasper‑nguftuq, tuunglighhaa sapphire‑nguftuq, pingayiitangat agate‑nguftuq, estamiitangat emerald‑nguftuq,
tallimiitangat onyx‑nguftuq, aghvinliitangat carnelian‑nguftuq, maaghraghvinliitangat chrysolite‑nguftuq, pingayuneng ingluliitangat beryl‑nguftuq, estamaneng ingluliitangat topaz‑nguftuq, quulngughutangat chrysoprase‑nguftuq, qula ataasiq siipniitangat jacinth‑enguftuq, qula maalghuk siipniitangat amethyst‑nguftuq.
Qula maalghuk siipneqluku amigllaget pearl‑nguftut, tamaghhaghmeng amigllaget ataasimeng pearl‑meng ulimaaghuftut. Neghllagem tuumngi gold‑eperegwaaghuftut; gold‑a meghraakegtepiglleghii siqinghwaaghtun.
Neghllagmi esghaanneghitunga Temple‑meng, qayughllak Temple‑nga Atanghuuq Kiyaghneq Aghtughyaghqaghhaanghilnguq, Penniighaghaaguqlu.
Neghllak siqineghsughniituq, nalighmeng tanqighsughniituq nighugkameng, qayughllak nighughqellgha Kiyaghneghem nighukegkanga, Penniighaghaqlu kenelghutaqegkanga.
Qamagtengngwaaghluteng nunam yugi kiyaghllequt nighugakun kuukgutngalghiikun. Nunamllu umiilgita aklungiteng tagiquutiit neghllagmun.
Neghllagem amigllagi umegnaanghitut aghneghem naangneghani qayughllak unugnaanghilnguq tamaani.
Nunam yugita neghllagmun tagiquulleqiit pinighnaghllaget aklungiteng.
Iwernga neghllagmun iteghyaghqaanghituq sangwaa seghleq, talwa kina alngunak seghleghnatun pista, nalighmeng iqlengiqesta. Iwernga neghllagmun iteghyaghqaagut tamaakunginaghhaat aatghit igaqngalghiit Igaakun Unguvallghem. Taakut Igat Penniighaghaam pikii.
Taagken yaqulgem kelguvikaanga kiiwegneng maaqelghiik Kiyaghneghemllu Penniighaghaamllu umiilgusigkenka aqumutagkeneng. Unguvallelitikayugmeng melgek, meghraakegtutkalghiik crystal‑etun.
Maaqngalghiik qukaakun tumangan neghllagem. Kiiwek inglugtun uqfigtuqak unguvallelitikayugneng. Tamaghhaghmi uqfik piitestikayuguuq fruit‑neng tanqiinaghqun, ayumiqulleghmi, ququngiitlu naallghutusiiftut nunataanun.
Sangwaa alngunak Kiyaghneghem nanqigtekaa aghyuughyaghqaaluku, neghllagmennaanghituq. Kiyaghneghenkuk Penniighaghhaankuk umiilgusik aqumutagket neghllagmesaghqaaguk, Kiyaghneghemllu qepghaghtengita manigughlleqaat.
Gginaa esghaghlleqaat, aatghallu qawiitgun igaqngallequq.
Tamaani unugnanighlleqaa, kenelghutaghsughniighulleqii, nalighmeng siqineghsughniighulleqii, qayughllak Ataneq Kiyaghneq nighukelleqaat. Igleghutillequtlu umiilguluteng quunperugllak kenlengunaan.
Tagilleghqaa Jesus‑emTaagken yaqulgem piinga, “Ukut akuzitet ugpeqsaghqaagut, ipanguutlu. Atanghem, Kiyaghneghem igleghutilghiim taghneghiitneng uuknaliqistemi, kayagtekaqaa yaquleni kelguvikesqelluki qepghaghteni sangwaat piyaghtungestaghniluki.”
Jesus piiq, “Nagatek! Tagiyaghtughtunga! Quyastekaagut qaatkullghiit uuknaliqelleghnun igaqngalghiinun ukutgun igatgun.”
Whanga, John, nagatkaqankallu esghaqaqankallu tamaakut. Nagaqughaqngamkillu esghaghaqngamkillu tamaakut, niinghutunga yaqulgem itegaani manigughnaluku, kelguvikisteka tamaaken.
Iwernga piinga, “Tawaten pigpenang! Whangallu qepghaghtenguunga elpetun, ugpeqaalgutegpetunllu uuknaliqistestun, qaatkullghiistunllu akuzitangitnun ukut igat. Manigughhu Kiyaghneq!”
Piingallu, “Aksaqegpenaki uuknaliqellghet ukut igat aapqiit, qayughllak tamaakut pilleghqiit kaasaghtuumaat.
Kina alngunak seghletun pilghii nagneghli seghletun, enkaam kina alngunak nukeggnameng suumqelghii nagneghli nukeggnameng suumqelluni. Kina alngunak elqughutngalghii nagneghli elqughutngaluni, kinallu alngunak pelungilnguq nagneghli pelungilluni.”
Jesus piiq, “Nagatek! Tagiyaghtughtunga! Akileghtuusaghqanka kelqelleqanka nallangightughnaluki yuget kiyaghtaallghistun.
Whanga Alpha‑nguunga Omega‑nguunga, whanga sivuliigunga kinguliigunga, whanga piinleghuunga kenlenguungallu.”
Quyastekaagut tamaakut atkuyaateng aghvikiit iqangiitesluki. Tamaaken apalluqluku neghyaghqaaghtekaagut piitestekaaneng unguvallelitikayugem uqfigem. Iteghyaghqaaghtekaagutlu neghllagem amigllagitgun.
“Whanga, Jesus, kayagtekaqaqa yaqulka elpesinun ugpeqanun yughaghvignilngughnun. Apeghlleqaak ukuk elpesinun, ‘Whanga David‑em kingunqaanga, whanga nighugrakegtaagunga unaangum ighaleqetaagha.’”
Taghneghaklu Ugiighnaqelghiillu piik, “Tagi!” Tamaghhaghmillu nagallghii pili, “Tagi!” Kina alngunak meqsulghii tagili; tuguklighligu akingilnguq meq unguvallelitikayuk.
NaangniitetWhanga, John, kelengasaaghyuganka nagallghiit uuknaliqelleghnun igaqegkatgun ukutgun igatgun. Kitum alngunak ilaraaqaki uuknaliqutkegkat ukuni igani, Kiyaghneghem aghyuughlleqaa. Ellnganun ilalleqii tamaakut seghleliilleghllaget igaqngalghiit ukutgun igatgun.
Kitum alngunak ikuvikegkaki uuknaliqutkegkat ukuni igani, Kiyaghneghem iqilleqii nengighqii piitestekat uqfiganeng unguvallelitikayugem. Kiyaghtesnaanghitaallu agleghnalghiimi neghllagmi. Taakuk apeghngaak ukuni igani.
Jesus‑nguuq aapghilghii tamaaken qamaglluteng ipanguniluki. Piiqlu, “Ipapestaaq tagiyaghtughtunga!”Amen. Tagi, Ataneq Jesus!
Nangllegtallgha Atanemta Jesus‑em tamaghhaghpesinilli. Amen.
